snippet.title: Solitaire Chronicles: Wild Guns
snippet.description: Saddle up for Solitaire Chronicles: Wild Guns and head out to the wild West! Shannon and Red Wolf have been astray for a while when they bump into a deserted town. For them, it's a chance to build themselves a home! Can you help them resurrect the settlement? Use the power of cards and match 3 to build a safe haven in Solitaire Chronicles: Wild Guns!
